# DBX Dual License

DBX is available under a **dual-license model**:

## üÜì Open Source License (MIT) - For Small Organizations

**You can use DBX for FREE under the MIT License if:**
- Your organization has **fewer than 100 employees**, AND
- Your annual revenue is **less than $5,000,000 USD**, AND
- Your external funding is **less than $10,000,000 USD**

See the MIT License terms below.

## üíº Commercial License - For Larger Organizations

**You need a Commercial License if your organization has:**
- **100 or more employees**, OR
- **Annual revenue of $5,000,000 USD or more**, OR
- **External funding of $10,000,000 USD or more**

**üìÑ See:** [LICENSE-COMMERCIAL.md](./legal/LICENSE-COMMERCIAL.md) for commercial license terms.

**‚ùì Not sure which license applies to you?** Read our [License Policy Guide](./legal/LICENSE-POLICY.md).

**üìß Contact us:** license@bytelogic.studio

